name: There is no place like home 2
description:
Cranberry Relational

There is no place like home if you're not there to stay. Bury your head in false facts, deny the cold, and stay away from the Hotel Amnesia, it's too much to be safe.

When in doubt, turn to the ether, there's no place like home if you're not there to stay.

Where figures from the past stand tall, mocking each other, whilom the coming storm. But you, little lamb, are but a rag caught in the maelstrom.


A merge of neural and artistic vision.
